[SN]TITLE[SN]
Taylor Wimpey leads FTSE 100 higher

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
(Close): Shares in Taylor Wimpey helped to lift the FTSE 100 after the housebuilder announced plans for a special dividend.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
